                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature disturbs the ashes in the fireplace or attempts to manipulate any of the evercursed crystals</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The crystals burn out, becoming non-magical stones, and the triggering creature must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:32|options:inflicts:dazzled,inflicts:blinded] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature's vision blurs and dims, and they become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Dazzled] for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, but with an unlimited duration.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] with an unlimited duration.</p>"
